value.name: Compete Against Popular TBS Programs! All-Star Prank Festival!
value.original_name: ＴＢＳ系人気番組対抗！オールスタードッキリ祭★芦田愛菜＆二階堂ふみ人生初の仕掛人
value.overview: This program is a prank festival in which the performers of the popular TBS program pull pranks on their co-stars, competing for fun and bonding within the program. Variety shows, news and information programs, and a new drama starting in January will also be participating
